## Installation

### Requirements
```python
# Python 3.8+ required
# Dependencies
numpy>=1.20.0
pandas>=1.3.0
scikit-learn>=1.0.0
pydantic>=2.0.0
```

### Install via pip
```bash
pip install tml-framework
```

### Install from source
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Lev-Goukassian/TML-Framework.git
cd TML-Framework
pip install -e .
```

### Verify installation
```python
import tml_framework
print(tml_framework.__version__)  # Should output: 2.0.0
