### Example Usage
```python
# Initialize with custom config
config = TMLConfig(
    max_complexity=0.8,
    min_confidence=0.6,
    stakeholder_weights={"patient": 0.4, "family": 0.3, "society": 0.3}
)

engine = TMLEngine(
    domain="healthcare",
